author: georgep
msg: TS-11: OpenSolaris_x86 (0906,5.11) port. This port supports both the 'libev' (level-triggered) and a native 'portfs' (edge-triggered) implementation. The code changes reflect patch TS11_osol_patch1.diff with suggestions from John P.
Tested: OpenSolaris(amd64,0906,5.11,gcc-dev-4/4.3.2,BerkeleyDB4.7), Ubuntu(x86_64,9.04), OSX (x86,10.5) and FreeBSD(amd64,7.2) with and without 'libev'
